{"title":"老汉卖余粮","authors":["梁平"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":9,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉卖余粮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚从收购站出来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉汗珠和喜悦一起往外冒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是多年没见的神情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他逢人便说：今年真好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多余的粮食粮站都收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有白条全是现钞……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶阳光很暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快嘴的夏蝉在树梢使劲叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——知了！知了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经很久了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉总在夏秋光临粮站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一次老汉都生气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一次都要背地里骂娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好生生的上等粮食"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一压再压"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除水除渣扣这扣那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到头还兑不了现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一挑粮食换一张白条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉看见好多人去找贩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贩子的绝招是现钞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上好的小麦稻谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗啦啦流进贩子的加工厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉心痛了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他问过粮站站长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知不知道粮食哪里去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站长满脸苦衷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表情似哭也似笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当过村支书的老汉认理儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每年余粮还是往粮站交"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚才站长说了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民有多少站里收多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一律不打白条！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉仰看晴朗的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日头当顶了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想起村口等他的乡亲们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔腿一路小跑……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}